## WHAT YOU CAN DO WITH THIS LICENSE

✅ **Single End Product**
- You can use the Item to create one single End Product for yourself or for one client (a "single application").
- The End Product must be a customized implementation of the Item for a specific customer/restaurant.

✅ **Modify the Code**
- You are licensed to use the Item to create one End Product for yourself or for one client, and you can modify the Item to suit your needs.

✅ **Commercial Use**
- You can use the Item to create an End Product that is used commercially (generates revenue).

✅ **Distribute the End Product**
- You can distribute the End Product to your client.

---

## WHAT YOU CANNOT DO WITH THIS LICENSE

❌ **No Redistribution or Resale**
- You can't re-distribute the Item as stock, in a tool or template, or with source files.
- You can't do this with an Item either on its own or bundled with other items.
- You can't re-distribute or make available the Item as-is or with superficial modifications.

❌ **No Multiple End Products**
- You can't use the Item to create more than one unique End Product.
- For multiple projects, you need to purchase a separate license for each End Product.

❌ **No SaaS Application**
- You can't use the Item to create an End Product that is sold or distributed as a SaaS (Software as a Service) application where users pay a subscription fee to access the functionality.
- For SaaS applications, you need an Extended License.

❌ **No Sublicensing**
- You can't sublicense the Item or any rights granted under this license.

