## DEFINITIONS

**Item**: The digital work (DeliveryOS - Food Delivery Management System) that you have purchased.

**End Product**: A customized implementation of the Item that is distributed to a single client or used by a single entity.

**End User**: A user of the End Product (restaurant staff, customers, drivers).

**Client**: The restaurant, business, or organization for whom you create the End Product.

